Creating Users in Windows 7

Control panel> User Accounts> Manage another accounts
>create a new account>"name"> standard or admin > create account


Pareantal controls

pick a usaer account> on / off 
time limits/games /allow or block specific program
ok


Notes
	Like win XP, you can use the user accounts applet or local
users and groups to manage user accounts

	Win Vista and win 7 add parental controls, enabling you to
control how and when certain accounts can be used

	remember the groups that are included with each version of
